  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You are not alone in the dark.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MOURNIGHT</strong> is a 1 to 4-player online co-op horror game where survival is your only goal.<br>A cursed mansion, locked doors, and something watching your every step...<br>Explore your surroundings, collect items, and don’t lose your light.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436970/extras/112a9206d2ef82edcf0603f013ee29c6.poster.avif?t=1758551468\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436970/extras/112a9206d2ef82edcf0603f013ee29c6.webm?t=1758551468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436970/extras/112a9206d2ef82edcf0603f013ee29c6.mp4?t=1758551468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A CURSED MANSION</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The curse of the Venedal Family has turned their home into a living nightmare.<br>Whispers echo through the walls, and unknown terrors await in every corner...<br>Escaping won’t be easy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436970/extras/e9f47de56a56a3ac4e7f335c8174d054.poster.avif?t=1758551468\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436970/extras/e9f47de56a56a3ac4e7f335c8174d054.webm?t=1758551468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436970/extras/e9f47de56a56a3ac4e7f335c8174d054.mp4?t=1758551468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>TOGETHER OR ALONE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play solo or with 2–4 players online.<br>Work together to unlock sealed rooms, discover hidden objects, and survive.<br>But beware: not everyone may make it out alive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436970/extras/a16da95c360b21e486ca5a949616ded9.poster.avif?t=1758551468\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436970/extras/a16da95c360b21e486ca5a949616ded9.webm?t=1758551468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436970/extras/a16da95c360b21e486ca5a949616ded9.mp4?t=1758551468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FIND BEFORE YOU’RE FOUND</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every corner might hide an item, a clue, or a disaster.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your light carefully, and hide the moment you hear the creature.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One wrong choice could be your last.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436970/extras/d375ac6dce8f07c92b6c3f4cef83680d.poster.avif?t=1758551468\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436970/extras/d375ac6dce8f07c92b6c3f4cef83680d.webm?t=1758551468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436970/extras/d375ac6dce8f07c92b6c3f4cef83680d.mp4?t=1758551468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Online co-op for 1–4 players</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A single intense map with limited resources</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find keys and items to unlock new rooms</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >High-tension survival horror experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Evolving through Early Access with community feedback</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Supported Languages:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >English</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turkish</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simplified Chinese</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Russian</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>...and more coming soon.</i></p></li></ul></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436970/extras/7a88af903e724b788dba5211c5aba44a.poster.avif?t=1758551468\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436970/extras/7a88af903e724b788dba5211c5aba44a.webm?t=1758551468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436970/extras/7a88af903e724b788dba5211c5aba44a.mp4?t=1758551468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hide.</strong><br><strong>Find.</strong><br><strong>Escape.</strong><br><i><strong>MOURNIGHT</strong> awaits you.</i></p>",
